data.eml:eml: Description of the female of Aysha yacupoi Brescovit 1992 (Araneae: Anyphaenidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Argañaraz, Carina I., Rubio, Gonzalo D., Brescovit, Antonio D. (2013): Description of the female of Aysha yacupoi Brescovit 1992 (Araneae: Anyphaenidae). Zootaxa 3652 (5): 582-586, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3652.5.7
